channel.title: Sneaky Dyce
channel.description:
Hello Guys, I'm Runescape-Xperia. I'm going to be making a dicing clan, me and my friend are making one.
[u][b]Introduction[/b][/u]
I've got 150 Million Gold Coins and rising everyday, my mate has a Yellow Partyhat and Max cash and he is willing to dice it all. We do [b]60x2[/b] and [b]we are legit and never scam[/b]. I'll post ranks below, also if you want to get higher in the clan you need to be [b]trusted[/b], [b]loyal[/b] and [b]active[/b]. We will ask you to pay for the first 5 ranks then when you are Lieutenant you will become a General after you are [b]trusted[/b], [b]loyal[/b] and [b]active[/b]. I hope you guys can come and join in all the fun. It's really fun and we are easy going and cool to talk to. Me, myself [b]Sneaky Lyre[/b] and my friend [b]Evil[/b] and hosting this and we hope everyone can come and join in the fun.
[b]Note:[/b] You must be a Lieutenant before you can get general and you'll most probably need to work up the ranks, depending on who you are the prices may vary.
[u][b]Ranks and Prices[/b][/u]
Recruit = 20 Million GP. Corporal = 35 Million GP. Sergeant = 60 Million GP. Lieutenant = 100 Million GP. Captain = 120 Million GP. General = Need to be Captain rank and be really good friends. Be [b]Loyal[/b], [b]Social[/b], [b]Active[/b], [b]Legit[/b] and [b]Trusted[/b].
[u][b]Worlds, Adds and Friends Chat[/b][/u]
We host in worlds 2 and 9, our hosts will be in either world. We don't add random people, we will only really have ranks and friends in our friends list. Not people we don't know and don't spam us. The friend chat that we use is [b]Sneaky Lyre[/b].
[b][u]YouTube[/u][/b]
http://www.youtube.com/user/SneakyDyce
[b][u]Rules and Regulations[/u][/b]
If you scam anyone or are caught out scamming you will be automatically banned from the clan chat and demoted of rank. But I hope this never happens because that would ruin our clans reputation. I want you to advertise this clan to all of your friends on Runescape and other forums and posted his topic on other forums. If you want to mess the owners around you'll lose your rank for 1-2 days. All dices must be recorded so if anything mucks up and people try and frame you for scamming you have proof. Watch out for intruders and warn other people, or you'll need to refund them or I'll sort it out.
